data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_5640376\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 07, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ddy1704180946739.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ddy1704180946739.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ddy1704180946739.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ihv1665702618350\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Reserved Keys on Microsoft Windows\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">It is possible to redefine the behavior of keys by editing the MSWINX keyboard translation table or using your own customized version. Such changes will affect the behavior of Unifields, but may be ignored by widgets.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\">For example:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27944e1_d27945e1_d27946e1\">In a multi-line edit box, <span class=\"ph keypress\">Page Up</span>, <span class=\"ph keypress\">Page Down</span>, <span class=\"ph keypress\">Up</span>, and <span class=\"ph keypress\">Down</span> arrows are handled by the widget and any redefinition in the translation table is ignored.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27947e1_d27948e1_d27949e1\">In a single-line edit box, the <span class=\"ph keypress\">Left</span> and <span class=\"ph keypress\">Right</span> arrow keys are also handled by the widget.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__p_d64514e1_d64515e1_d64516e1\">The following keys are reserved by Microsoft Windows and should not be redefined in Uniface:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27950e1_d27951e1_d27952e1\">Alt\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27953e1_d27954e1_d27955e1\">Alt+Escape\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27956e1_d27957e1_d27958e1\">Alt+F4\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27959e1_d27960e1_d27961e1\">Alt+Hyphen\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27962e1_d27963e1_d27964e1\">Alt+Insert\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27965e1_d27966e1_d27967e1\">Alt+PrintScreen\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27968e1_d27969e1_d27970e1\">Alt+Spacebar\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27971e1_d27972e1_d27973e1\">Alt+Tab\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27974e1_d27975e1_d27976e1\">Control+Escape\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27977e1_d27978e1_d27979e1\">Control+F4\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27980e1_d27981e1_d27982e1\">Control+F6\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27983e1_d27984e1_d27985e1\">Control+Shift+F6\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27986e1_d27987e1_d27988e1\">Control+Insert\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27989e1_d27990e1_d27991e1\">Control+Tab\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27992e1_d27993e1_d27994e1\">Delete\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27995e1_d27996e1_d27997e1\">F10\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d27998e1_d27999e1_d28000e1\">Insert\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d28001e1_d28002e1_d28003e1\">Home\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d28004e1_d28005e1_d28006e1\">End\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d28007e1_d28008e1_d28009e1\">Page Up\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d28010e1_d28011e1_d28012e1\">Page Dn\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d28013e1_d28014e1_d28015e1\">Control+Alt+Delete\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d28016e1_d28017e1_d28018e1\">Control+Alt+Shift+Delete\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d28019e1_d28020e1_d28021e1\">PrintScreen\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d28022e1_d28023e1_d28024e1\">Shift+Alt+Tab\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d28025e1_d28026e1_d28027e1\">Shift+Delete\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d28028e1_d28029e1_d28030e1\">Shift+Insert\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d28031e1_d28032e1_d28033e1\">Shift+Home\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d28034e1_d28035e1_d28036e1\">Shift+End\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d28037e1_d28038e1_d28039e1\">Shift+Page Up\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ihv1665702618350__li_d28040e1_d28041e1_d28042e1\">Shift+Page Dn\n </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dya1704180540707.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Keyboard Support on Microsoft Windows</a><p>Many Uniface applications, including the Uniface IDE, run on Microsoft Windows platforms. Uniface provides the MSWINX keyboard translation table(KTT) as default to handle keyboard input on this platform. This translation table follows Windows conventions for navigation, and cut, copy, and paste actions.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5640376\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5640376\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Reserved Keys on Microsoft Windows Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 07, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Reserved Keys on Microsoft Windows It is possible to redefine the behavior of keys by editing the MSWINX keyboard translation table or using your own customized version. Such changes will affect the behavior of Unifields, but may be ignored by widgets. For example: In a multi-line edit box, Page Up , Page Down , Up , and Down arrows are handled by the widget and any redefinition in the translation table is ignored. In a single-line edit box, the Left and Right arrow keys are also handled by the widget. The following keys are reserved by Microsoft Windows and should not be redefined in Uniface: Alt Alt+Escape Alt+F4 Alt+Hyphen Alt+Insert Alt+PrintScreen Alt+Spacebar Alt+Tab Control+Escape Control+F4 Control+F6 Control+Shift+F6 Control+Insert Control+Tab Delete F10 Insert Home End Page Up Page Dn Control+Alt+Delete Control+Alt+Shift+Delete PrintScreen Shift+Alt+Tab Shift+Delete Shift+Insert Shift+Home Shift+End Shift+Page Up Shift+Page Dn Related Links Keyboard Support on Microsoft Windows Many Uniface applications, including the Uniface IDE, run on Microsoft Windows platforms. Uniface provides the MSWINX keyboard translation table(KTT) as default to handle keyboard input on this platform. This translation table follows Windows conventions for navigation, and cut, copy, and paste actions. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}